envalysis 0.2.0
======================

NEW FEATURES
* `texture` class for automatic determination of particle size distribution using a hydrometer in accordance with ASTM D422-63(2007)e2

MINOR IMPROVEMENTS
* updated `theme_publish()`
* demo file added

